Market Analysis and Size

The recent developments in the field of automation and the self-directed functions in automobiles are being increasing adopted globally. The recent innovations and developments provided by the VANET (Vehicular Ad Hoc NETwork) states that the vehicles have been employed with the notifications related to the crash, prior warning with respect to the accidents, construction on the roads, over speed and others. The highly reliable and reduced accidental rates of the robot trucks and cars have led to greater demands worldwide, and this factor will boost the market's growth over the forecasted period.

